Ralph Faulkner https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ralph_Faulkner 0 Ralph Faulkner (July 20, 1891 – January 28, 1987) was an American fencer and film actor. He competed in the team sabre event at the 1932 Summer Olympics. Ralph_Faulkner ( July_20_,_1891 – January_28_,_1987 ) was an_American_fencer_and_film_actor . He competed in the_team_sabre_event at the_1932_Summer_Olympics .
